{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought to say that I have got a toothache.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he pushed through my eardrum, and that I got the relief from the middle-ear infection.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I wasn't-- I wasn't taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it took a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't have time to feel sorry for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One have to go to work just the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but-- in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the girls were so good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were teams.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all the same age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they saw what's happening, one was always looking out the window to see if the German didn't come, so, you know, I wouldn't have to work so hard.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there are certain things we had to do in a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't just leave it for tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, a laundry was closed up because they took laundry-- the German laundry-- out to the German quarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they got some Ukraine girls or something, they were working then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was transferred to do laundry-- the Jewish laundry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was so hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh, gosh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought I wouldn't last long in that laundry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time with-- with the water, and the wet, and the steam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I don't know why we had to work there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- what--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boiling the shirts because they wanted us to-- to keep clean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had sheets over our straw in the-- in the-- where we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That has to be washed and all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Frenzel was a Sturmbannfuhrer who was in charge when [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wagner ?] was on holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came in and asked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I can't make a whole shirt, but during the war I learned somewhere to make collars and cuffs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
